com.danielbchapman.groups

Class Groups

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.danielbchapman.groups.Groups

  • public class Groups
extends java.lang.Object
    The manager class provides a set of static methods to access a set of groups. Each group is designated by its unique name and its serialization. In general each group is just a lump sum of String data.
    Author:
    Daniel B. Chapman
